==Hardware:==

===Precursor vaporizer===
#Crucible : This holds a pre measured quantity of precursor
#Crucible lid: This screws onto the crucible and ends in a barb fitting, connecting the crucible to the tubing that carries PC gas to the mixing chamber
#Hot plate: The crucible is placed on the hot plate to heat it to specified temperature
#Nitrogen bottle with regulator: Purge gas

===Tubing, fittings and valves===
#Tubing: Chemically inert polypropylene tubing is used 
#Ball valve: Used as a shutoff valve to start and stop flow of gas
#Needle valve: Used to regulate flow of gas

